{"tid":1156063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲總理：中國是客戶 美國是朋友   中國網友氣炸","createTime":"2019-05-15T11:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T15:00:00.000Z","uid":28765,"like":393,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"51a6ec6267b971ebb4faa8aa48af744d03a0330b","tid":1156063,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T11:10:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpeg0Vbt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpeg0Vbt.jpg&h=f0c7ba93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳洲總理莫里森（Scott Morrison）日前對記者表示「中國是客戶，美國是朋友」。（美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n2019-05-15 13:29<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕澳洲總理莫里森（Scott Morrison）日前對記者表示「中國是客戶，美國是朋友」，這句話引發澳洲華人社區反對，中國網友在網路上也紛紛辱罵澳洲「欠收拾」。<br />\n<br />\n《美國之音》報導，莫里森當時表示澳洲不需要在美國與中國之間選邊站，「要站在朋友的一邊，但也要站在顧客的一邊」。對此反對黨砲轟，美澳是盟友，但對中國稱為客戶並不適當，澳洲華人區也對莫里森說法表達不滿。<br />\n<br />\n中媒也報導該則新聞，底下網友則是一面倒地罵聲，痛斥「錯了，中國是你大爺」、「意思是可以大把的掙中國的錢，然後著美國再一起反對中國」，但也有人說「看來現任總理是個老實人啊，還算不錯，其實我知道大部分澳洲人的真實想法是中國是敵人」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2790619\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2790619&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2MorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=b5840fce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2790619&h=eb82c649\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2790619</a>"},{"pid":"89d30d58143dac891e9978de3ea362681ca3302d","tid":1156063,"uid":38777,"like":201,"dislike":0,"score":201,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T11:12:02.000Z","msg":"中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14fabb0c6c1d583882bb44c600a52336bf8f7df2","tid":1156063,"uid":228955,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T11:12:14.000Z","msg":"底L死 死支那"},{"pid":"4f7202d65a60732954c4765cf111654efec97c61","tid":1156063,"uid":237562,"like":